<br>
Change content so that completing it is not only possible....it makes sense to do so from a character point of view. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#33333><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title><A HREF="http://www.ezboard.com/promotions/csc.html" TARGET="_blank" ><IMG SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/image/cscicon3.gif" WIDTH="20" HEIGHT="20" BORDER="0" align="absmiddle"></A> <A HREF=http://pub140.ezboard.com/bgraffeswizardcompilation.showUserPublicProfile?gid=whizbangdustyboots>Whizbang Dustyboots</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elder Arcanist<BR>Gnomus Originalus</span><br>  Posts: 12896<br> <font color=#ffffff>(5/18/03 6:56 pm)</font><br>     <br>ezSupporter<br> </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Back Burner&quot;</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr> and what was so unfinished about LOY?<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END-->You remember the storyline that lead up to the expansion, a storyline important enough to evict the trolls from the home they've had since beta? That story? The story of the Stone From Beyond, which two clans of trolls battle over, to &quot;change the face of Norrath&quot; with?<br>
